Example Parameter Table

example_parameter_table.Rd

Example dataset containing parameters for SQUID analysis.

Usage

Format

A data frame with 133 rows and 17 columns:

Characteristic unique ID

CHR_NAME

Characteristic name

WQS_NAME

Water quality standard name

SortOrder

Sort order for display

ShortName

Short name for parameter

ShortNameOLD

Previous short name

Units

Units of measurement

USE

Designated use category

ATTAINS_NAME

ATTAINS name

ATTAINs_GROUP_ID

ATTAINS_GROUP_NAME

ATTAINS group name

ATTAINS_ID

ATTAINS identifier

ADB_NO

ADB number

ADB_NAME

ADB name

CAS

STORET

STORET code

SHORT_CAUSE_NAME

Short cause name
